ActNational Round Table on the Environment and the Economy Act
PrecisAppointment of FRANKLIN A. HOLTFORSTER of Ottawa, Ontario, to be a member of the National Round Table on the Environment and the Economy, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective November 9, 2009, in the place of Mark Jaccard.
